{"tid":2385213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國有人發起雪球大戰被罰款一萬英鎊","createTime":"2021-01-29T02:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T02:41:43.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b43cb00ef9ec90938c31fe75be9b40fadec8bd37","tid":2385213,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"Two men who organised a mass snowball fight during the latest coronavirus lockdown have each been fined &pound;10,000.<br />\n<br />\nHundreds descended on Hyde Park in Leeds when heavy snowfall carpeted the city earlier this month.<br />\n<br />\nWest Yorkshire Police said the men, aged 20 and 23, had put those who took part or watched at &quot;a significant and completely unnecessary risk&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nCh Supt Damien Miller said the event on 14 January had been a &quot;blatant breach&quot; of the rules.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We take absolutely no pleasure in handing out such heavy fines to these two young men, but their actions encouraged hundreds of people to be in close proximity to each other,&quot; he said.<br />\n<br />\nThe 23-year-old had previously received a fine for breaching restrictions on mixing households, the force said.<br />\n<br />\nPolice declined to give any further details about how the men encouraged people to attend the snowball fight.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-leeds-55845582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-leeds-55845582&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=a3a0b7c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-leeds-55845582&h=64591f11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-leeds-55845582</a>"},{"pid":"1b1000e5d6a712f160eb8aa61778f3b750dc99a3","tid":2385213,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif